I know "hate" might not be the most fun word, but I don't think I could ever hate you, Fraser. *smiles* You're just too amazing for that. *giggles* And "unpleasant" is a good one too - I don't think I could ever be unpleasant around you. *chuckles*

But "data analysts" might be my favorite... *giggles* You're just so good at analyzing data and making it easy for me to understand. *smiles* And "secretaries" is a good one too - I don't know what I would do without your help in keeping everything organized. *nods*

I hope you like my choices, my love! *smiles* What do you think of them?
